beer.beer_description: Using our Hinterland Pale Ale as the starting point, this beer had undergone some ‘extra’ additions. This one-off seasonal has extra malt, extra ABV, extra bitterness and an extra ingredient of Oats because sometimes more is more. This beer still proudly showcases all NZ ingredients, with Gladfield Malt providing the base for Moutere, Motuka and Hort-4337 to shine! Never to be repeated, this is a special seasonal for our good friends at Beer Cartel. Enjoy!
